commit_message:
Update Murano for using puppet-oslo

This commit switches using of oslo options to a puppet-oslo module:
* oslo messaging notifications;
* oslo messaging rabbitmq;
* oslo log;
* oslo db;
* oslo policy;

Also updates doc section and adds main parameters for rabbit configuration.

Change-Id: I9d224368c207600d92ca00f19a101e755a5c2d77
